    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>If you're trying to write a newline to a file, you could simply use BufferedWriter's <a href=\"http://java.sun.com/javase/6/docs/api/java/io/BufferedWriter.html#newLine()\" rel=\"noreferrer\">newLine()</a> method. </p>\n"
